Advantages of approach in question 1: 
The advantages of this approach are that it follows the traditional MVC model, which means the application is easy to mantain, it provides an easy way to update and sustain
thee application, and it allows developers to work in an efficient manner. 

Disadvantages of approach in question 1: 
The main disadvantages of this approach are that the updates can make the system complex, and each component of the MVC model is not versatile. 
